Explained vs. Unexplained Variation

\[ \begin{aligned}
Y_i - \overline{Y} & = (Y_i - \hat{Y}_i) + (\hat{Y}_i- \overline{Y})\\
\text{Total unexplained variation} & = \text{Residual variation after regression} + \text{Variation explained by regression}
\end{aligned}\]

